      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know there are hotlines... but they don't change the fact that the house is empty. it feels like i'm just performing the motions of a person. i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize myself anymore. it's like i'm just waiting for something to happen, but nothing ever will. everything just feels so... pointless. like there is no version of the future where this actually feels okay again.",
